### Variables
@baseUrl = http://localhost:5000/api
@authToken = PASTE_YOUR_JWT_TOKEN_HERE

### 1. Register a New User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Mahboob Iqbal",
    "email": "mahboob@example.com",
    "password": "securepassword123",
    "phone": "03001234567"
}

###

### 2. Login User
POST {{baseUrl}}/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "email": "mahboob@example.com",
    "password": "securepassword123"
}

###

### 3. Get User Profile (Protected Route)
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/profile
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 4. Submit Easypaisa Deposit TID (Protected Route)
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/deposit
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 2500,
    "transactionId": "EP1234567890"
}
### ==========================================
### PHASE 3: WALLET & TRANSACTION TESTING
### ==========================================

### 4. Submit an Easypaisa Deposit TID
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/deposit
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 5000,
    "transactionId": "EP9988776655"
}

###

### 5. Request a Cash Withdrawal
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/withdraw
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "amount": 1500,
    "targetPhone": "03459998877"
}

###

### 6. Select an Investment Plan
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/select-plan
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "planName": "Plan B"
}

###

### 7. Fetch My Transaction Ledger History
GET {{baseUrl}}/wallet/transactions
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 8. Manually Trigger Daily ROI Profit Distribution (Development Testing)
### In production, this will run automatically every 24 hours via cron scheduler. 
### For testing: ensure user has an active plan (not 'None') and approve any pending deposits.
### Returns: profit calculations and updated balances for all users with active plans.
### Plan A: 2% daily profit, Plan B: 3.5% daily profit, Plan C: 5% daily profit.
POST {{baseUrl}}/wallet/trigger-daily-roi
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

### ==========================================
### PHASE 5: USER PROFILE & SETTINGS TESTING
### ==========================================

### 9. Get Main Dashboard Aggregated Statistics
GET {{baseUrl}}/auth/dashboard-stats
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}

###

### 10. Update User Password (Security Settings)
PUT {{baseUrl}}/auth/update-password
Authorization: Bearer {{authToken}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "currentPassword": "securepassword123",
    "newPassword": "myBrandNewPassword2026"
}